Package cscie55.hw6

Main package with solution for hw #6

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ATM
    Interface that contains the methods that the ATM can perform.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    Class representing the account of one client.
    ATMImplementation
    Class that implements the ATM interface.
    ATMInputStream
    Class that represents an input stream for the ATM distributed application.
    ATMProxy
    ATM Proxy is a class that enables the client to dispatch each method of the ATM interface to the remote ATMImplementation.
    ATMRunnable
    Class responsible for executing client requests and sending the response to the corresponding client.
    ATMThread
    Thread class used to execute client requests concurrently.
    Client
    Class that represents a client that makes remote transactions with an ATM server.
    Server
    Class that represents an ATM server for client requests.
